moji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你打去法律諮詢問差人既野<br />\n<br />\n我真係笑左出黎<br />\n<br />\nBtw,報警未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n柒咗你就潛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n柒到我無眼睇落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f14e91d0ee46bf2b418e0afef017eef6cc7a2c","tid":224554,"uid":45713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:20:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>尋晚瞓唔著打去啲廿四小時免費法律諮詢到問，佢專做刑事案件個啲嘅，笑到我死，個法律諮詢講咗以下呢幾點：<br />\n1.邊有觀塘pass去將軍澳，由將軍澳pass返去觀塘就有，因為觀塘係總區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.不誠實使用電腦係一條副例嚟，無得就咁單獨告<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3.就算佢事後俾返張影返張口供紙俾當事人，當事人都係唔可以影嚟放上網，係咩資料都唔得，因為係要保密架。<br />\n4.真係pass咗去CID到，佢事後俾返個個檔案編號個張卡仔個當事人，張卡仔上面應該係應該會有寫係CID第幾隊，但蔣囝影出嚟張卡無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5.張口供紙十成九都係假嘅<br />\n唔好咁on9啦，下次作都作得好啲啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你打去法律諮詢問差人既野<br />\n<br />\n我真係笑左出黎<br />\n<br />\nBtw,報警未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n柒咗你就潛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n柒到我無眼睇落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37